{
  "stem": "18186.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I only remember only this one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of my sisters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother went to, I think-- was he going Cheder or not?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my father was a butcher, and he had a kosher butcher shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were stores that you-- stores that you could buy kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly single families.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our house was-- was considered large.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was two bedrooms, large size, big living room, nice-sized kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we had a big garden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had-- cows, chickens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had other things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had-- I couldn't-- it was considered as a nice size house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Also, my father's butcher shop was with the-- it's at the house, sort of like.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he brought the animals at the outside, you know, the Gentile people were selling the animals.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were raising animals that-- for selling them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we had the slaughter house, which a shochet came, and they slaughtered the-- the kosher meats.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Slaughter, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside a little bit was, in the school, Polish, Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the main language was, in my parents' house, Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The grownup, too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I was too young to know that anti-Semitism is something, you know-- there's such a thing like anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I really-- I know-- I knew one thing that when we were in school, everybody stick to their own-- own--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kind, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were the Jewish kids were with the Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Gentile kids were with the Gentile.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even the Ukrainian and the Polish didn't mix.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So everybody stuck to their own thing, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in class-- this was after the class-- in class, we sat together, mixed.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
